data.description:
Stop by and preview this well kept starter home located in the desirable community of Villa Valencia. This home
is 1,790 sq. ft with 4 bedrooms, 2 baths, a perfect fit for a small family. Open layout concept with a great room
is inviting for quality time with family and friends. Master bedroom is spaced out perfectly for peace and privacy which leads
to the master bathroom with bath tub and shower separate.
The backyard landscape is an oasis for any gardener with custom planters ready to grow your favorite plant life. The aluminum 
pergola and stamped concrete adds a nice modern, sleek touch outdoors. Make this quaint home yours!
